{"tid":32042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港視股價曾升55%","createTime":"2016-12-10T03:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T04:35:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e93c1f9860b04afbd12d8bbfa7073f81587022e2","tid":32042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161210/19860940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161210%2F19860940&d=IKE5B3xalFjF69%2F32X2WuXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ebb57b49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161210%2F19860940&h=298c2760\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161210/19860940</a><br />\n<br />\n港視股價曾升55%<br />\n<br />\n11,717<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n ■港視股價升，王維基昨在fb叮囑網民「開心還開心，不能掉以輕心」。資料圖片<br />\n■港視股價升，王維基昨在fb叮囑網民「開心還開心，不能掉以輕心」。資料圖片<br />\n【本報訊】特首梁振英向來被視為阻攔香港電視（1137）獲發免費電視牌照的最大障礙，昨日港視於梁振英宣佈不參選下一屆特首的半小時內，一度急升55%，最終全日收市升33.3%，收報1.64元，創3個月新高，公司市值漲至3.3億元。<br />\n王維基：勿掉以輕心<br />\n港視主席王維基昨亦於facebook回應，表示「這個周末，香港人可以開心一點了。但，開心還開心，不能掉以輕心，記住有些『大話精』說話從不算數。如果你以為今天贏了，那明年3月就是輸了。我們不單要換特首，更要有全民普選的民主制度」。<br />\n王維基又呼籲「大家記住12月11日出來投票，合力捍衞非建制派的300票！這300票，足以左右明年3月的特首選舉結果」。<br />\n2013年10月，梁振英會同行政會議拒絕港視的免費電視牌照申請，外間戲稱為「一男子」因素，指梁是港視不獲發牌的最主要原因。<br />\n除了港視昨日大升外，部份傳媒股如壹傳媒（282）、有線（1097）等股價都上升，而立場傾向政府的星島（1105）及鳳凰衛視（2008）均下跌，《明報》母公司世界華文（685）則跌10%。<br />\n■記者石永樂  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n房策無能　樓價飆劏房增<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n「梁粉」鄭家純感可惜"},{"pid":"f742df0bbc99b40ac83d0bd2f28ef116d30276c4","tid":32042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:49:48.000Z","msg":"■港視股價升，王維基昨在fb叮囑網民「開心還開心，不能掉以輕心」。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161210/large/10la4p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F10la4p10.jpg&h=6e603b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66987dd6ae2c87be4de18fe28a7dbcb55c32f353","tid":32042,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c83bcd0b1e915349fd3bb380b48299100965de7","tid":32042,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc1ae719ba37a83c74f355e8d7eb6c7189ef5c26","tid":32042,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩用<br />\n佢間野仲蝕緊錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n升翻過招股價先講啦"},{"pid":"7b1804e97481f71689339621a74c3170713a71f7","tid":32042,"uid":42909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得<br />\n其實換咗特首<br />\n佢都唔會有牌"}]}